{
  "stem": "26142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would lay one kind of [HEBREW] and [INAUDIBLE] until after the [HEBREW] and then they would take these [HEBREW] off and put on another set of [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One is the set that's [HEBREW], and these are called [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's not important right now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But very, very pious and religious Jews would do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most of them would not do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I used to see that, for instance, my father wouldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I used to see we had our rabbi, the [HEBREW], you know, those that were making a living in the congregation as religious leaders, they would observe these things.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he started screaming, he said, I'm sorry, I'm sorry all my life that I laid two pairs of [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Throw the [HEBREW] away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Throw the tallit away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was starting like-- like blasphemy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I looked at that and this is-- this is the type of Jew that would say something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It turned out, he found out that he somehow lost his daughter and a child that was-- that was-- he escaped and he lost in a-- in a few days.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How he got to our group, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Maybe he came a day later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Or I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyway, that's why-- why I-- I said that it had-- now, these-- this woman and the two daughters and the son that were-- were living in Budapest, they were completely assimilated.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, they didn't know anything about Judaism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember, they started-- started asking us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It had an opposite effect on them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, the, the-- the conflict was resolved that most of the people stopped praying and we started-- we started going-- going in the direction back to the-- to the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
